---
// src/pages/index.astro
// Evonic Landing Page — Swarm Intelligence, Zero Lock-in
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="evonic-landing">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Evonic — Swarm Intelligence, Zero Lock-in</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Your Models. Your Rules. Your Swarm. Local-first agentic AI for open models.">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg-deep: #020617;
      --bg-navy: #152A3A;
      --bg-navy-light: #1B394F;
      --accent: #818cf8;
      --accent-glow: #667eea;
      --accent-warm: #764ba2;
      --text-primary: #f1f5f9;
      --text-secondary: #94a3b8;
      --text-muted: #64748b;
    }

    html { font-size: 16px; scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg-deep);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }

    /* ── Background layers ── */

    .bg-mesh {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .bg-mesh::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -40%;
      left: -20%;
      width: 140%;
      height: 140%;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 20%, rgba(21, 42, 58, 0.9) 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 50%, rgba(27, 57, 79, 0.7) 0%, transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 80%, rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 70%, rgba(118, 75, 162, 0.1) 0%, transparent 45%);
      animation: bgFloat 20s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }

    .bg-mesh::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 30%, rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.06) 0%, transparent 40%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 10% 60%, rgba(27, 57, 79, 0.4) 0%, transparent 50%);
      animation: bgFloat 15s ease-in-out 5s infinite alternate-reverse;
    }

    @keyframes bgFloat {
      0% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
      100% { transform: translate(2%, -1%) scale(1.05); }
    }

    .dot-grid {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 40px 40px;
    }

    .page-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    /* ── Topbar ── */

    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .topbar-link {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .topbar-link:hover {
      color: var(--accent);
      background: rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.08);
    }

    /* ── Hero ── */

    .hero {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .mascot-wrapper {
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .mascot-glow {
      position: absolute;
      inset: -40px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.2) 0%, rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.08) 40%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: glowPulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes glowPulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1); }
      50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.1); }
    }

    .mascot {
      position: relative;
      width: 200px;
      height: auto;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.3));
      animation: mascotFloat 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes mascotFloat {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-8px); }
    }

    /* ── Tagline ── */

    .tagline {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .tagline-main {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .tagline-main .highlight {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-warm));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .tagline-sub {
      font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem);
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .tagline-sub .brand {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    /* ── CTA ── */

    .cta-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-family: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.25s;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-glow), var(--accent-warm));
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 6px 30px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.5);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-ghost {
      background: rgba(27, 57, 79, 0.5);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      border: 1px solid rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.2);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .btn-ghost:hover {
      background: rgba(27, 57, 79, 0.8);
      border-color: rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.4);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    /* ── Features ── */

    .features-section {
      padding: 2rem 2rem 5rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .features-label {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .feature-card {
      background: rgba(27, 57, 79, 0.35);
      border: 1px solid rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.1);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
      background: rgba(27, 57, 79, 0.65);
      border-color: rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.3);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: block;
    }

    .feature-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .feature-card p {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* ── Footer ── */

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem 3rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* ── Responsive ── */

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .topbar { padding: 1rem 1rem; }
      .hero { padding: 1rem 1rem 3rem; }
      .mascot { width: 150px; }
      .features-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
      }
      .features-section { padding: 1rem 1rem 3rem; }
      .feature-card { padding: 1.25rem 1rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="bg-mesh"></div>
  <div class="dot-grid"></div>

  <div class="page-content">
    <nav class="topbar">
      <a href="/getting-started/installation" class="topbar-link">Docs</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/anvie/evonic-docs-site" class="topbar-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
    </nav>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="mascot-wrapper">
          <div class="mascot-glow"></div>
          <img
            class="mascot"
            src="/img/mascot.png"
            alt="Evonic Mascot"
            width="200"
            height="auto"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="tagline">
          <h1 class="tagline-main">
            <span class="highlight">Swarm Intelligence</span>,<br/>Zero Lock-in.
          </h1>
          <p class="tagline-sub">
            Your Models. Your Rules. <span class="brand">Your Swarm.</span>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-group">
          <a href="/getting-started/installation" class="btn btn-primary">
            Get Started &rarr;
          </a>
          <a href="/system" class="btn btn-ghost">
            Explore Docs
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="features-section">
        <p class="features-label">Core Principles</p>
        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🔓</span>
            <h3>Open Model First</h3>
            <p>Built for open models. Zero vendor lock-in — run any model, anywhere, locally.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🤝</span>
            <h3>Agent-to-Agent Protocol</h3>
            <p>Agents talk directly to each other. No orchestrator bottleneck. True swarm intelligence.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🪶</span>
            <h3>Minimal Dependencies</h3>
            <p>Lean stack. No bloated abstractions. Just what you need to run agents at scale.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">🛡️</span>
            <h3>Isolated Execution</h3>
            <p>Every agent runs in its own sandbox. Secure by default, no cross-contamination.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="feature-icon">⚡</span>
            <h3>Fast &amp; Reliable</h3>
            <p>Optimized for speed. Async-first architecture built for production workloads.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <p>Evonic &copy; 2026 &mdash; <a href="https://github.com/anvie/evonic-docs-site">Open Source</a> AI Agent Framework</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
